ory of the Barber Pole</h3>\n                </article>\n\n                <!-- Article 4 -->\n                <article class=\"group cursor-pointer\">\n                    <div class=\"aspect-[4/3] bg-neutral-800 rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-4\">\n                        <img src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1605497788044-5a32c7078486?q=80&amp;w=1000&amp;auto=format&amp;fit=crop\" class=\"w-full h-full object-cover group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-500 opacity-80 group-hover:opacity-100\" alt=\"Face Shapes\">\n                    </div>\n                    <span class=\"text-xs font-medium text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-wider\">Style</span>\n                    <h3 class=\"text-lg font-medium text-white mt-2 group-hover:text-neutral-300 transition-colors\">Choosing the Right Cut for Your Face Shape</h3>\n                </article>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- FAQ Section -->\n    \n\n    <!-- Footer -->\n    <footer id=\"contact\" class=\"bg-neutral-950 border-t border-white/10 pt-16 pb-8\">\n        <div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\">\n            <div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16\">\n                <!-- Brand -->\n                <div class=\"col-span-1 md:col-span-1\">\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-white tracking-tighter block mb-6\">EMPIRE</a>\n                    <p class=\"text-neutral-500 text-sm mb-6\">Premium grooming for the modern gentleman in Tallaght.</p>\n                    <div class=\"flex gap-4\">\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-neutral-400 hover:text-white transition-colors\">\n                            <iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:instagram\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></iconify-icon>\n                        </a>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-neutral-400 hover:text-white transition-colors\">\n                            <iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:facebook\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></iconify-icon>\n                        </a>\n                        <a href=\"#\" class=\"text-neutral-400 hover:text-white transition-colors\">\n                            <iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:twitter\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"></iconify-icon>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Contact Info -->\n                <div class=\"col-span-1\">\n                    <h4 class=\"text-white font-medium mb-4\">Contact</h4>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-3 text-sm text-neutral-400\">\n                        <li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\">\n                            <iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:map-pin\" class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0\" width=\"16\"></iconify-icon>\n                            <span>Unit 3 High St, Tallaght,Dublin, D24 PW71</span>\n                        </li>\n                        <li class=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                            <iconify-icon icon=\"lucide:phone\" class=\"shrink-0\" width=\"16\"></iconify-icon>\n                            <span>(01) 561 6665</span>\n                        </li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Hours -->\n                <div class=\"col-span-1\">\n                    <h4 class=\"text-white font-medium mb-4\">Opening Hours</h4>\n                    <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-400\">\n                        <li class=\"flex justify-between\">\n                            <span>Mon - Fri</span>\n                            <span class=\"text-white\">09:00 - 18:30</span>\n                        </li>\n                        <li class=\"flex justify-between\">\n                            <span>Saturday</span>\n                            <span class=\"text-white\">09:00 - 18:00</span>\n                        </li>\n                        \n                    </ul>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- CTA -->\n                <div class=\"col-span-1\">\n                    <h4 class=\"text-white font-medium mb-4\">Ready for a cut?</h4>\n                    <p class=\"text-xs text-neutral-500 mb-4\">Book online to secure your slot.</p>\n                    <a href=\"#book\" class=\"inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded bg-white py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-950 transition-colors hover:bg-neutral-200\">\n                        Book Appointment\n                    </a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"border-t border-white/5 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center text-xs text-neutral-600\">\n                <p>© 2024 Empire Barbershop. All rights reserved.</p>\n                <div class=\"flex gap-4 mt-4 md:mt-0\">\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-neutral-400\">Privacy Policy</a>\n                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-neutral-400\">Terms of Service</a>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body></html>","language":"html","username":"3d801dc3-9ab7-4a0c-a361-3deb77b863e1","created_at":"2026-01-23T18:57:44.212398+00:00","views":525,"image_url":"https://hoirqrkdgbmvpwutwuwj.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/preview-images/shared-code-previews/barbershop-landing-13-preview-1770857090361.jpeg","forks":11,"private":false,"watermark":true,"featured":true,"share_source_code":true,"user_id":"3d801dc3-9ab7-4a0c-a361-3deb77b863e1","category":"Mobile","updated_at":null,"tags":["Landing Page","Services","Brand","Dark","Gradient","Large Type","Minimal","3D","Barbershop","Hair Salon"],"description":"A premium barbershop website template for showcasing services, pricing, reviews, and online bookings for modern grooming studios.","premium":false,"price":null,"purchase_url":null,"long_description":"**Empire Barbershop Landing Page Template** delivers a sleek, dark, and modern one-page experience tailored for barbershops and grooming studios.\n\n## Highlights\n- **Hero with 3D background** and bold headline to capture attention instantly.\n- **Service grid and price list** for showcasing cuts, shaves, and premium packages.\n- **Online booking-focused CTAs** like “Book Appointment” placed in navbar, hero, and footer.\n- **Testimonials section** to build trust with ratings and client quotes.\n- **Journal/blog layout** for grooming tips, style insights, and culture articles.\n- **Contact, hours, and location** clearly presented in a polished footer.\n\nUse this template to quickly launch a brand-forward barbershop site that highlights your craftsmanship, communicates pricing transparently, and drives more online bookings.","custom_domain":null,"favicon_light_url":null,"favicon_dark_url":null,"dns_verified":null,"dns_verified_at":null,"dns_a_record":null,"netlify_apex_exists":null,"netlify_www_exists":null,"netlify_verified_at":null,"custom_domain_added_at":null,"netlify_site_id":null,"umami_website_id":null,"umami_share_id":null,"analytics_enabled":false,"gtm_container_id":null,"remix_source":{},"credit_remix_source":false,"search_visibility":"aura_and_custom_domain"}]